1
00:00:37,300 --> 00:00:40,580
=Reincarnated Love=

2
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:43,700
=Episode 13=

3
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,590
Mr. and Mrs. Huo,

4
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,870
by the time we found him,

5
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,040
he was already dead.

6
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,870
We have no idea what happened.

7
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,560
We didn't hear any sounds either.

8
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,680
We rushed over
right after Jiang Huaikang

9
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:40,430
was imprisoned.

10
00:01:41,230 --> 00:01:42,350
We were only a step too late,

11
00:01:42,870 --> 00:01:44,070
and he was killed.

12
00:01:45,230 --> 00:01:46,350
It's too suspicious.

13
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,950
(The Lotus on the handkerchief...)

14
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:06,790
Ruoli,

15
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,790
are you alright?

16
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:29,150
(Is everything related to Lu Huaijin?)

17
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,710
(If it truly was him,)

18
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,240
(why would he kill Jiang Huaikang?)

19
00:03:59,030 --> 00:03:59,870
Ruoli.

20
00:04:00,870 --> 00:04:01,710
Ruoli,

21
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,430
are you all right?

22
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,710
It's all my fault.

23
00:04:09,710 --> 00:04:11,360
I shouldn't have startled you.

24
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:13,590
Yanzhi,

25
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:16,830
did you visit Hanyan Temple
ten years ago,

26
00:04:17,390 --> 00:04:19,560
and save someone back then

27
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,920
just like today?

28
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,400
Yes.

29
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:29,790
It was you.

30
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:32,480
Were you the one who saved me

31
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,360
that year?

32
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,940
ظآزGentle rain seeps into the deep nightظآز

33
00:04:36,940 --> 00:04:39,080
ظآزStirring the jasmine from slumberظآز

34
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:43,040
ظآزTwo swallows nest upon the beamظآز

35
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,770
ظآزBringing fresh mud for the homeظآز

36
00:04:46,910 --> 00:04:49,240
ظآزGazing afar at the roadside
that I once knewظآز

37
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:52,040
ظآزLush grass swayed in abundanceظآز

38
00:04:52,930 --> 00:04:56,560
ظآزThough beauty abounds,
it answered not your callظآز

39
00:04:56,570 --> 00:04:57,410
Yuan.

40
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,760
Yuan, wake up.

41
00:04:59,310 --> 00:05:00,560
Yuan, wake up.

42
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,510
Yuan...

43
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,830
Yuan, wake up.

44
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,000
Wake up.

45
00:05:07,040 --> 00:05:07,950
Wake up.

46
00:05:10,290 --> 00:05:11,920
ظآزThat same gentle smileظآز

47
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,080
Back then,

48
00:05:14,870 --> 00:05:17,070
I remember you wearing a yellow dress.

49
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,750
When you fell into the water,

50
00:05:20,493 --> 00:05:21,950
you looked like a little yellow duck.

51
00:05:21,970 --> 00:05:24,600
ظآزI gift you a sprig of jasmineظآز

52
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:25,720
It's really you.

53
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:28,140
ظآزTogether from dawn till duskظآز

54
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:30,160
It's been you all along.

55
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,240
After all these years,

56
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,600
I mistook someone else for you.

57
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:40,090
ظآزThat year's urgent meeting
in a city of drifting petalsظآز

58
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,360
At Hanyan Temple, it was me.

59
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,100
Today, it's me as well.

60
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,830
Through lifetimes,

61
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,750
it was all me.

62
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:52,750
ظآزTrue to the heart, clear in intent,
two souls as oneظآز

63
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:55,370
ظآزWith you, winter feels less coldظآز

64
00:05:55,370 --> 00:05:58,860
ظآزDeep feelings are hardest to healظآز

65
00:05:58,860 --> 00:06:01,520
ظآزThe closer I get,
the more I long for youظآز

66
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:05,870
ظآزMy heart stirs, awake and drawn inظآز

67
00:06:06,210 --> 00:06:12,610
ظآزThe touch on my ear tells me it's youظآز

68
00:06:21,140 --> 00:06:25,420
(Virtue Sustains All)

69
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:29,070
(The one who saved me
was Huo Linchuan,)

70
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:31,510
(so Lu Huaijin...)

71
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,760
Ruoli,

72
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,480
you just fell into the water.

73
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,480
You might catch a cold sitting here.

74
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,240
Yunzhou,

75
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:42,240
you still worry about me as before.

76
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:44,870
All these years, that hasn't changed.

77
00:06:45,270 --> 00:06:47,510
But Yanzhi couldn't even protect you.

78
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,190
Why still let things get tangled
with him?

79
00:06:51,830 --> 00:06:52,830
That's true.

80
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:56,270
He's not as gentle and caring as you.

81
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,870
I once fell into the water as a child.

82
00:06:59,870 --> 00:07:02,120
Luckily, you came to my rescue
just in time.

83
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,830
That was all long ago.

84
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,680
Back then, you were just a child.

85
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,360
You swallowed water and were terrified.

86
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:13,070
On your way back with the Chancellor,

87
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:14,430
you kept trembling in his arms.

88
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,720
(I never expected this.)

89
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:19,720
(Lu Huaijin has fooled me
all these years.)

90
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,870
(She's testing me.)

91
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:42,430
(Could she already know?)

92
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,480
Wake up, Yuan.

93
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:45,710
Wake up.

94
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,840
Wake up.

95
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,350
Wake up.

96
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,630
Yunzhou.

97
00:08:11,430 --> 00:08:13,000
Yuan, you're awake.

98
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,270
(I can't wait any longer.)

99
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:24,950
(Huo Linchuan)

100
00:08:25,270 --> 00:08:26,750
(must be gotten rid of soon.)

101
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,600
(If Lu Huaijin)

102
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,630
(is the mastermind behind all this,)

103
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,240
(what will he do next?)

104
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:09,830
ظآزThe dream shatteredظآز

105
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:11,870
ظآزLike illusion, yet trueظآز

106
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,510
ظآزLike a restless soulظآز

107
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:15,950
ظآزHow vagueظآز

108
00:09:16,350 --> 00:09:17,870
ظآزRain and blood, drifting wildظآز

109
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:20,110
ظآزA blade of frost in dreamsظآز

110
00:09:20,910 --> 00:09:23,510
ظآزLove and hate entwinedظآز

111
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:26,830
ظآزRise and fall, yet never fadeظآز

112
00:09:27,470 --> 00:09:32,230
ظآزHow can I turn the tides
of this fleeting lifeظآز

113
00:09:32,830 --> 00:09:34,350
ظآزWhen fate falls apartظآز

114
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:38,310
ظآزMemories return,
carving tears upon my faceظآز

115
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,590
ظآزYet I can't hold onظآز

116
00:09:40,990 --> 00:09:44,710
ظآزOnly warmth remains
where longing once burnedظآز

117
00:09:45,430 --> 00:09:48,270
ظآزLife after lifeظآز

118
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:51,430
ظآزFated to meet, but never meant to beظآز

119
00:09:52,070 --> 00:09:56,150
ظآزStill, I refuse to bow or yieldظآز

120
00:09:56,230 --> 00:09:59,270
ظآزIn this life, love becomes my bladeظآز

121
00:09:59,430 --> 00:10:00,830
ظآزTo break free from reincarnationظآز

122
00:10:00,830 --> 00:10:03,950
ظآزAll past affairs tangled with regretظآز

123
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:05,470
ظآزNow shatter apartظآز

124
00:10:05,590 --> 00:10:09,350
ظآزBy fate and karmic ties confinedظآز

125
00:10:10,070 --> 00:10:12,870
ظآزIs this fate or calamityظآز

126
00:10:13,150 --> 00:10:15,990
ظآزIs it life, death, or parting painظآز

127
00:10:16,310 --> 00:10:20,710
ظآزI ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heartظآز

128
00:10:20,950 --> 00:10:23,870
ظآزIn the next life, grant me one kissظآز

129
00:10:23,990 --> 00:10:28,430
ظآزTo kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gazeظآز

130
00:10:28,630 --> 00:10:34,350
ظآزFor once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never partظآز

131
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:37,510
ظآزThis fleeting life feels but a dreamظآز

132
00:10:37,750 --> 00:10:40,470
ظآزSober or indulgeظآز

133
00:10:40,910 --> 00:10:46,910
ظآزI only wish to be with you,
with all my heartظآز
